  Closed on Statutory holidays and long weekends.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Website: http://centrefornewcomers.ca/ " VerticalAlignment="Top" Width="364" TextChanged="TextBox_TextChanged" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="14">
